Port                   22
LoginGraceTime         20
PermitRootLogin        without-password
AuthorizedKeysFile     .ssh/authorized_keys
PasswordAuthentication no
UseDNS                 no
Subsystem              sftp /usr/lib/ssh/sftp-server
ClientAliveInterval    60   # keep client from disconnecting automatically
ClientAliveCountMax    10   # if there's no activity, close the session after 10min
